snippet.title: Blood Nova Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Blood Nova is out! Blood Nova is a new sci-fi fantasy 2D point and click adventure game. 

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1810270/Blood_Nova/
On Fireflower Games: https://fireflowergames.com/products/blood-nova
Or Itch: https://cosmicvoid.itch.io/blood-nova

Follow us on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/Cosmic_Void_
https://twitter.com/RossJosephG

Music by Donovan Jonk [MegahammerAudio]:
https://twitter.com/MegahammerAudio
